            "value": "<p>Fey whimsy or a tryst in a moonlit grove put the bewitching magic of the First World into your family's bloodline.</p>\n<p><strong>Tradition</strong> primal</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Skills</strong> Deception, Nature</p>\n<p><strong>Sorcerous Gifts</strong> cantrip @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Figment], 1st: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Charm], 2nd: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Laughing Fit], 3rd: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Enthrall], 4th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Suggestion], 5th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Hallucination], 6th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Mislead], 7th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Visions of Danger], 8th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Uncontrollable Dance], 9th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Metamorphosis]</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Spells</strong> initial: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Faerie Dust], advanced: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Fey Disappearance], greater: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Fey Glamour]</p>\n<p><strong>Blood Magicâ€”Cloak of Ribbons</strong> Colorful fey ribbons dance around you. Either you gain a +2 status bonus to Performance checks for 1 round, or you can become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Concealed] for 1 round. Such obvious concealment can't be used to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Hide]</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.Effect: Fey Blood Magic]</p>"
